NG-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 20px; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体, SimSun; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><strong style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(204,0,0); PADDING-TOP: 0px">3.</strong><span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px">&nbsp;钱、货需客户当面点清，离开提货前台后将不再对钱、货数量负责；</span></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></li><li style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><p style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 20px; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体, SimSun; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><strong style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(204,0,0); PADDING-TOP: 0px">4.</strong>&nbsp;<span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px">货物价保需客户在自提当场提出，离开提货前台后不再对自提货物提供价保服务；</span></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p></li><li style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><p style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 21px; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 20px; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体, SimSun; PADDING-TOP: 0px"><strong style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(204,0,0); PADDING-TOP: 0px">5.</strong>&nbsp;<span style="PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px">普通发票：由库房开具发票，随包裹一同发送，自提